@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### POST /signup — enqueue a welcome email job (runs immediately in background)
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "carol@example.com"
}

###

### POST /remind — schedule a welcome email 5s from now
POST {{baseUrl}}/remind
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "dave@example.com"
}

###

### GET /stats — queue stats (pending, running, failed counts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/stats
